         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">August 21st 1886. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you that four of the students of Botany ¶ Emily Coundon, Thomas Day, Margaret Douglas, Mary Amy Lee (The School of Mines Ballarat. Annual Repor...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">86.08.21b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Andrew Berry</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter press copy book, p. 103, School of Mines and Industries, Ballarat, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">August 21st 1886.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you that four of the students of Botany<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Emily Coundon, Thomas Day, Margaret Douglas, Mary Amy Lee (<seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">The School of Mines Ballarat. Annual Report 1886</seg>, Ballarat, 1887, p. 60).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have notified their intention to present themselves as Candidates for The School's Certificate of competency in that subject at the forthcoming examinations on the 18th September proximo</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>And by direction to ask you, as Examiner, to be so good as to prepare and forward at your convenience a paper of questions for examination of the Candidates<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For reply, see M to A. Berry, 24 August 1886<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 86-08-24a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Andw Berry</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Registrar</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir Ferdinand von Mueller K.C.M.G.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
